        {
            "name": "Iffdahsil",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "The slithering horror known as Iffdahsil is an undead <a aonid=\"368\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">shoggoth</a> that has haunted the vault of the Black Desert for millennia. <a aonid=\"37\" game-obj=\"MonsterFamilies\">Drow</a> legends in particular tend to feature Iffdahsil, terrifying the elves from a young age.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Aberration</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"11\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Occultism</a></u>)</b>: DC 52<br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Undead</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"13\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Religion</a></u>)</b>: DC 52",
