                "text": "60 feet, DC 45. A creature entering or starting its turn in the aura that fails at a Fortitude save becomes <a aonid=\"9\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">doomed 1</a> and <a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">drained 1</a>. If the target was already doomed or drained, the values of these conditions increase by 1, to a maximum of doomed 3 and drained 3. A creature that dies while doomed 3 and drained 3 in this way disintegrates into black sand."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "ability",
                "ability_type": "automatic",
                "name": "Unkillable",
                "traits": [
                    {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
