                            "alt": "occult",
                            "game-obj": "Traits",
                            "aonid": 120
                        }
                    }
                ],
                "text": "Unlike most undead, Iffdahsil isn't destroyed at 0 HP. Iffdahsil's fast healing continues to function normally, though on any round it begins its turn at 0 HP, it is <a aonid=\"13\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">enfeebled 4</a> and <a aonid=\"35\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">slowed 1</a> until the start of its next turn. While Iffdahsil is at 0 HP, it can be killed permanently only by simultaneously exposing it to direct sunlight (or a 10th-level <a aonid=\"326\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>sunburst</i></a> spell) and casting a <a aonid=\"196\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>miracle</i></a> or <a aonid=\"377\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>wish</i></a> spell (or similar magic) directed at destroying it."
            }
